{"tid":1610742,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我地下一步要做嘅係明修棧道，暗渡陳倉","createTime":"2019-10-01T19:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:17:27.000Z","uid":80972,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"520002fdf818429a43370b021a594cbe6a015711","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:34:26.000Z","msg":"民主、自由、和平一路都係西方世界嘅普世價值，但你要知鬼佬其實係幾咁虛偽。特別係世界警察美國，成日都高舉民主、自由，然後就拎支軍隊去打人地，守住起度就話和平。伊拉克個薩達姆都係咁俾老美推翻，出兵原因都係9up。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對於老美，以前香港嘅價值係賺中國人錢，而家係用香港黎搞鳩中國。</span>要好好發揮現有價值，我地就應該<span style=\"color: red;\">明修棧道，暗渡陳倉</span>。雖然呢8個字老套d，但係好實用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明修棧道 <br />\n五大訴求，講到口都臭，港共又唔理，國際傳媒都唔會再講太多。要老美再進一步支持，國際傳媒繼續關注香港，訴求應該提升到國際同外交層面。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">宣布中英聯合聲明失效，要求聯合國暫時接管香港，中英重新談判。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之前都有英美議員出黎講話中英聯合聲明已經失效，邊個講你地自己google。鬼佬最講合約精神，當年美國睇小中共，由得英國傾條垃圾聲明出黎。而家實唔會放過呢個機會，用條合約，搞死中共。Trump trump自己都話中共要守，而家<span style=\"color: red;\">我地就要向佢求救，話中英聯合聲明已經失效，要求重新談判</span>。到時又要傾貿易戰，又要傾聯合聲明，睇中共點死。<br />\n<br />\n理由大把，我講幾個<br />\n- 由中共控制的政府，3個幾月未有回應民主訴求<br />\n- 港人治港，高度自治已經失去<br />\n- 未有落實基本法上所列明的民主普選<br />\n- 紅色企業全面入侵，聯合王國(UK)和其他國家在香港的經濟利益未得到照顧<br />\n- 中共粗暴DQ民主議員，干預及破壞香港的立法權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地應該有班人高調出黎同老美等西方國家做場大龍鳳，美國同西方國家俾到中共壓力，就算傾唔成功，五大訴求，清算黑警都會指日可待。<br />\n<br />\n暗渡陳倉就夠1000個回覆先講。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復</span>香港<br />\n時代<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"15dedabef7f93c478c2662799759a3dd2b49582a","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:35:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d0cb797b4008134eb88802a45db0b5aca2093ee8","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:35:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec95a4cdc20be2ec42f794bdd9893ec7bfbb5c18","tid":1610742,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:36:59.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4c822adb4f5be5022dabf55eefa0bc2131196d4b","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97f5a27bec017dfd1f97c7cc0f1b7f0ac44b86ae","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:41:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a6f9ecf38f0e71cbdefce9e003a4b3f791ff381a","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:42:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ee360e56287800ec11e824a838b08a353b75485f","tid":1610742,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mj0sqKG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMj0sqKG.png&h=ff313d6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CY6rGh1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCY6rGh1.png&h=14044725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rUetakb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrUetakb.png&h=bb50a2d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31747616b622805c5efc6a5c2fd257ddd0b57f95","tid":1610742,"uid":142010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:56:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">輕輕一推</span>"},{"pid":"af97a68f5b051ac68d3b114acea232336d682420","tid":1610742,"uid":228701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:09:44.000Z","msg":"1. 寫正經文章表述立場（G20、攬炒）<br />\n2. 煽情文宣將香港抗爭英雄化<br />\n3. 用政治漫畫（變態辣椒、Cuson）醜化敵人<br />\n4. 聯合外國左翼整啲靚嘅活動（摺紙、唱歌）<br />\n<br />\n4肯定唔會令革命成功，<br />\n但非常重要。<br />\n要令外國人自我感覺良好。<br />\nSupport HK=文明人<br />\nSupport China=野蠻人<br />\n減慢外國赤化速度，<br />\n逼政客同中國保持距離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武提供材料，<br />\n和理非用各種手段推上國際。<br />\n香港人自己爭取民主，<br />\n同時必須爭取全球圍堵中共，<br />\n支爆到冚家剷香港先會有一線生機。"},{"pid":"3f15155926eeb0f59b07a25876b3c75fdac62e0b","tid":1610742,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jv4XZAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjv4XZAM.jpg&h=1150a5d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【SUCK小隊】 【10.2】 【三罷】 之 【狼來了】  【SUCK塞】【SUCK商場】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1610403/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1610403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手推POST呀!!!"},{"pid":"2fad082d329cd917093c9c4b91331a52a41d1630","tid":1610742,"uid":26726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:17:58.000Z","msg":"講得幾好 幫推"},{"pid":"e5a3015398452d2857bfd22d59c1a7e9919e6e1f","tid":1610742,"uid":207122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:19:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12f9881dbba8e444bde17b897c50ec996f5e5c34","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:37:28.000Z","msg":"起身繼續自推"},{"pid":"be3450d95a01da905210d262ccaf540608fb90ae","tid":1610742,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:38:50.000Z","msg":"而家香港係一個誰大誰惡誰正確既時代<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"82917bbcc473a6a9ae36ba9081e2efb8760e4ba8","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:39:35.000Z","msg":"push again"},{"pid":"66a7a44f601b4a20df862bf772fa0bbb275f5cc0","tid":1610742,"uid":10737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:39:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4689eb51638cc9a5d0b350d07c91b9f0f5702b7","tid":1610742,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:39:57.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"f1d2e99650c40c18e44b6736ad4569563bde5d91","tid":1610742,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:42:57.000Z","msg":"開宗名義<br />\n<br />\n反枱，起圍，革命，獨立"},{"pid":"d098aa34791fd505836624c73bf6663adbfdc8a3","tid":1610742,"uid":225281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"}]}